Object

类 Object

  • java.lang.Object
    • Object.Object
  • 直接已知子类:
    Aircraft, Explosion, ExternalLoad, GunBullet

    public class Object
extends java.lang.Object
    class Object defines an object with view and Physical properties it has x,y location, velocity, mass and can excute operations such as move and accelerate Its Subclass include Aircraft, ExternalLoad, GunBullet and so on
    作者:
    WangShuzheng
